  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to FLAC</title>

    <para><application>FLAC</application> is an audio CODEC similar to
    MP3, but lossless, meaning that audio is compressed without losing any
    information.</para>

    &lfs65_checked; <!-- compiled with NASM 2.07 -->

